                                                "20": {
                                                  "id": "20",
                                                  "speaker": "Karlach",
                                                  "text": "Even I'm not thick enough to fall for the same trick twice. But keep it up, kid, and you'll be scamming with the greats in no time.",
                                                  "context": "NodeContext: Lighthearted, ribbing the kid. This is a goodbye. After this, Karlach and the kid disengage and the player addresses karlach.",
