                                                        "2": {
                                                          "id": "2",
                                                          "speaker": "Karlach",
                                                          "text": "It is, isn't it. Hope he makes it out of this mess with his wits in one piece. I'd like to see him set up in a proper home in the city. Every kid deserves that.",
